---
description: 'Prefer Bun built-in helpers for file operations when using Bun runtime'
alwaysApply: false
---

This monorepo uses **Bun** for package management and scripts (`bun install`, `bun run …`). Prefer Bun built-in helpers in scripts: `Bun.file()` for reading, `Bun.write()` for writing, `Bun.file().exists()` for checking existence. Use `Bun.hash`, `Bun.password`, etc. when available.
